subSubSection.paragraph:
Remarks. This species is similar to
Tetra sinicae
Li, Wei & Wang, 2006
, but can be differentiated by coxal area with granules (coxal area smooth in
T . sinicae
), dorsal annuli with faint microtubercles (dorsal annuli smooth in
T . sinicae
), female genital coverflap with 2 transverse lines at base (female genital coverflap smooth at base in
T . sinicae
).
